          "treatment": "Tacrolimus: target trough 5-10 ng/mL after 3 months. MMF 500-1000 mg BID. Prednisolone wean by 3-6 months. Monitor for NODAT, dyslipidemia, infection. Annual DSA. Cancer screening (skin, cervical, breast/colon per age). Vaccinations (inactivated)."
