          "treatment": "CMV: reduce immunosuppression if feasible. Ganciclovir/valganciclovir. BKV: reduce immunosuppression (especially tacrolimus + MMF). Wait for immune recovery. Monitor PCR weekly. Leflunomide/cidofovir for persistent BKV."
        },
        {
          "severity": "malignancy/PTLD",
          "criteria": "post-transplant lymphoproliferative disorder, skin cancers",
          "treatment": "Reduce immunosuppression (stop MMF/azathioprine, reduce CNI). Rituximab for CD20+ PTLD. Chemotherapy for refractory. Skin cancer: sunscreen, annual dermatology. Switch to mTOR-I (sirolimus/everolimus) with antiproliferative and anticarcinogenic effects."
        }
